---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <main class="container mx-auto p-4 md:p-8 max-w-4xl relative z-10 pt-24">
        <h1 class="text-4xl text-white font-bold drop-shadow-md mb-8 text-center">About Me</h1>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr] gap-8 items-start">
            <!-- Profile Card -->
            <div class="bg-white/90 p-6 rounded-xl border-4 border-choco shadow-xl flex flex-col items-center">
                <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-sky mb-4 bg-sky/20">
                    <img src="/nakako.png" alt="Nakako" class="w-full h-full object-contain pixelated" />
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-choco mb-2">Nakako</h2>
                <p class="text-choco/80 text-sm mb-4">Freelance Engineer</p>
                <div class="w-full h-1 bg-choco/10 mb-4"></div>
                <p class="text-choco/90 text-left text-sm leading-relaxed w-full">
                    札幌を拠点に活動するフリーランスエンジニア。<br>
                    どちらかというとフロントの方が好き。<br>
                    でも頼まれたらなんでも頑張ってやります。
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Skills & Bio -->
            <div class="space-y-8">
                <!-- Tech Stack -->
                <div class="bg-white/80 p-6 rounded-xl border-2 border-white shadow-lg backdrop-blur-sm">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-choco mb-4 border-b-2 border-dashed border-choco/30 pb-2">
                        Tech Stack
                    </h3>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        {['React', 'Astro', 'TypeScript', 'TailwindCSS', 'MicroCMS', 'Firebase', 'Unity'].map((skill) => (
                            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-sky/20 text-choco font-bold rounded border-b-2 border-sky/50 hover:translate-y-0.5 active:border-b-0 transition-all cursor-default">
                                {skill}
                            </span>
                        ))}
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Bio / Message -->
                <div class="bg-white/80 p-6 rounded-xl border-2 border-white shadow-lg backdrop-blur-sm">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-choco mb-4 border-b-2 border-dashed border-choco/30 pb-2">
                        Biography
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-choco text-lg leading-relaxed">
                        実際に仕事で使ったことあるのはJavascript(React)、Java(SpringBoot)、Python(FastAPI)、PHP(Laravel)などなど。
                        趣味でNext.jsとかUnityとか少し触ってます。<br>
                        好きなAIはGeminiで、いつも一緒にコーディングしています。<br>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
            <a href="/" class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-choco text-white rounded hover:bg-choco/90 transition-colors">
                ← Back to Top
            </a>
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Cloud Background (Reused) -->
    <div class="fixed inset-0 z-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
        <div class="cloud absolute top-20 right-[10%] w-32 h-12 bg-white rounded-full opacity-60 animate-float-slow"></div>
        <div class="cloud absolute top-40 left-[5%] w-24 h-10 bg-white rounded-full opacity-40 animate-float-medium"></div>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    .pixelated { image-rendering: pixelated; }

    /* Reused Cloud Styles (Ideally move to global or component) */
    @keyframes float {
        0% { transform: translateX(0); }
        50% { transform: translateX(20px); }
        100% { transform: translateX(0); }
    }
    .animate-float-slow { animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite; }
    .animate-float-medium { animation: float 5s ease-in-out infinite reverse; }

    .cloud::before, .cloud::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        background: inherit;
        border-radius: 50%;
    }
    .cloud::before { width: 50%; height: 150%; top: -50%; left: 15%; }
    .cloud::after { width: 50%; height: 120%; top: -40%; right: 15%; }
</style>
